{"tid":1468724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地啲後生仔淨係識得搞亂個社會","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T21:46:07.000Z","uid":2947,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"102656fbc41181284da437007f4e84d32e9fb4b0","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:19:09.000Z","msg":"今朝搭車，聽個司機向師奶抱怨，話有年輕人顧住玩手機唔叫落車。講講下就講到後生仔搞搞震，搞亂社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家好常聽到<span style=\"color: red;\">後生仔+搞搞震</span>呢個組合<br />\n又唔會有人話醫生律師有份搞亂架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解呀？因為對家唔會提呀！<br />\n連醫生律師都支持仲得了嘅，咁佢地到底係好人定壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係說服老一輩嘅關鍵，對老人家/中年人嚟講，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">專業人士講嘅嘢不嬲最有說服力</span><br />\n<br />\n依家好多中年人，老人家都覺得係後生仔搞搞震。<br />\n後生仔已經被貼上<span style=\"color: red;\">搞破壞嘅標籤</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都好大機會因為呢個標籤流失咗一部份人嘅支持。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要令今次<span style=\"color: red;\">唔再似係年輕人嘅政治運動</span>，<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\">全民參與</span>呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣可以多啲提及，<br />\n反修例運動係有好多<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同年齡層</span>嘅人參與，<br />\n仲要好多係<span style=\"color: red;\">專業人士</span>！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係老人家，師奶最信任嘅醫生護士（權威人士）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令佢地有所動搖，思考自己立場係啱定錯已經對我地有利！！<br />\n<br />\n第一次出post，未必講得清晰睇得透徹，希望大家明白我想表達嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969e5e8a372122ad4d2bbf1f2907eec244fb290c","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:20:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5767d006ccbc70ce5ed69038dcc053387a3fb36","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:20:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa21e2c553ba7a64c7220e3a3499635084b1a2a","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:20:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7355271c684f5784aabce281ceb449fbdb0deb","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d71a012cd92d634ea738a3a81e2007b9f1faa2a","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:20:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"138a702551d34422951fd123385292eb144f11ca","tid":1468724,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c466052a156ac0b175e3981c8af889b3f0a80bb8","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:21:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97d865f7b700a6107fb7718d90701d25c6e8a550","tid":1468724,"uid":2947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:21:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"452c802bd48b899aee506fa2c67a13c46e395c4d","tid":1468724,"uid":81214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:07.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"2870bda72774da7094f998dcd0931e4a8f6d7a20","tid":1468724,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:20.000Z","msg":"瞓唔著推多推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd639b7f653818d8a14d3474a9ed3a0f104ffac","tid":1468724,"uid":246762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473dc86e2ef7f774477e24e76d1c415aeb0af8f4","t